oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and split fountain, dark blue to blue, on white) announcing the 2006 Nashville Star Tour featuring Chris Young, Casey Rivers, Nicole Jamrose, and Matt Mason at the MTSU (Middle Tennessee State University) Murphy Center on August 28. Poster features a woodcut of a crowd.
